  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the salt block to 145°F (63°C) using a sous-vide machine.",
    "Season the beef stock cubes with salt and black pepper.",
    "Heat the olive oil in a large pot over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the shallots and garlic and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the fennel and carrots and cook until they begin to soften, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the cumin, coriander, and red pepper flakes and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the red wine vinegar and beef stock cubes and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook until the vegetables are tender, about 20 minutes.",
    "Stir in the pine nuts and chopped parsley.",
    "Serve the tagine hot, garnished with additional parsley if desired."
  ],
